- · Water:  Implementation  of  the  roadmap  with  the  ambition  to reduce water consumption in our distilleries by 20% by 2030;
- · Responsible  drinking:  Pernod  Ricard's  strategic  brands  will launch marketing campaigns focusing on responsible drinking, with a goal of ramping them up each year over the next five years;
